                    The Directorate of Research and Supplies was established in 1987 and has multi-dimensional scope. The ultimate aim was to lay a strong foundation for a healthy human society. The directorate is consistently trying to improve cattle, sheep, goat and poultry industry through scientific management & planning. In the year 2019, Directorate of Research & Supplies was upgraded to Directorate General of Research & Supplies.
                </p>
