                    <li>
                        <p class="list">Provision of veterinary training in animal breeding & genetics, nutrition and livestock management</p>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <p class="list">Experimentation and propagation of indigenous sheep breed through selective breeding</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="list">Involvement of women in Livestock rearing activities as trained para-veterinary staff</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="list">Development of sheep, goat, dairy and poultry industry by using scientific technique</p>
                    </li>



                    <li>
                        <p class="list">Poverty elevation through distribution of backyard poultry birds on subsidized rates</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="list">Preservation of pure sheep breeds present in Balochistan province</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
